https://help.sonatype.com/en/download.html --> Link to get nexus download, Always use link to download

Steps to lauch Nexus:
1.Launch a Server and open in command prompot
2.go to root user
3.go to otp directory --> cd /opt/
4.Install latest version of Java --> yum install java-21-amazon-corretto -y
5.Download nexus, Navigate to link and copy link address and download --> wget <Link address>
6.unzip the downloaded file --> tar -zxvf filename.zip
7.check the files what are downloaded --> ll
8.then create user --> useradd ravi
8.Change the owner for downloaded files --> chown -R ravi:ravi filename filename (we need to change owners for both nexus and sonatype)
9.Go to nexus file --> cd nexusfilename/
10.Go to Bin directory --> cd bin/
11.start the nexus --> ./nexus start
